trans-unit.source: Represents controls that act as containers for a collection of child elements.
trans-unit.target: Representerer kontroller som brukes som beholdere for en samling av underordnede elementer.

trans-unit.source: The children of this element support <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern"></xref> and are organized in a two-dimensional logical coordinate system that can be traversed by row and column.
trans-unit.target: Underordnede til støtte for dette elementet <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern"> </xref> og ordnes i et todimensjonal logiske koordinatsystem kan traversert av rad- og.

trans-unit.source: This control pattern is analogous to <xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridPattern> with the distinction that any control that supports TablePattern also exposes a column or row header relationship, or both, for each child element.
trans-unit.target: Denne kontrollen mønsteret tilsvarer <xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridPattern>med forskjellen at alle kontroller som støtter TablePattern også viser en kolonne eller rad overskrift relasjon eller begge deler, for hver underelement.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridPattern>

trans-unit.source: Controls that support the TablePattern control pattern also support the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridPattern> control pattern in order to provide access to the inherent grid functionality of a table.
trans-unit.target: Kontroller som støtter TablePattern kontrollen mønsteret også støtte av <xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridPattern>kontrollen mønsteret for å gi tilgang til innebygd rutenett-funksjonalitet i en tabell.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridPattern>

trans-unit.source: See [Control Pattern Mapping for UI Automation Clients](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) for examples of controls that may implement this control pattern.
trans-unit.target: Se [kontrollen mønsteret tilordning for Brukergrensesnittet automatiseringsklienter](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) for eksempler på kontroller som kan implementerer dette mønsteret for kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the cached [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] property values for this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TablePattern"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter den bufrede [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] egenskapsverdier for dette <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TablePattern"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Cached property values must have been previously requested using a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest>.
trans-unit.target: Bufret egenskapsverdier må tidligere er forespurt ved hjelp av en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest>

trans-unit.source: Use <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TablePattern.Current%2A> to get the current value of a property.
trans-unit.target: Bruk <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TablePattern.Current%2A>å hente gjeldende verdi for en egenskap.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.TablePattern.Current%2A>

trans-unit.source: For information on the properties available and their use, see <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TablePattern.TablePatternInformation>.
trans-unit.target: For informasjon om egenskapene som er tilgjengelige og bruken, kan du se <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TablePattern.TablePatternInformation>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.TablePattern.TablePatternInformation>

trans-unit.source: A structure containing the cached [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] property values for the control pattern.
trans-unit.target: En struktur som inneholder den bufrede [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] egenskapsverdier for kontrollen mønsteret.

trans-unit.source: The requested property is not in the cache.
trans-unit.target: Den forespurte egenskapen er ikke i hurtigbufferen.

trans-unit.source: Identifies the property that gets the collection of column headers for a table.
trans-unit.target: Identifiserer egenskapen som henter kolonneoverskrifter-samlingen for en tabell.

trans-unit.source: This identifier is used by UI Automation client applications.
trans-unit.target: Denne identifikatoren brukes av Brukergrensesnittet Automation klientprogrammer.

trans-unit.source: UI Automation providers should use the equivalent field in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TablePatternIdentifiers>.
trans-unit.target: Brukergrensesnittet Automation leverandører må bruke det tilsvarende feltet i <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TablePatternIdentifiers>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.TablePatternIdentifiers>

trans-unit.source: The order of the headers returned will be consistent within a provider, but not necessarily across providers.
trans-unit.target: Rekkefølgen på hodene returnerte blir konsekvent i en leverandør, men ikke nødvendigvis på tvers av leverandører.

trans-unit.source: This property is not present in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TablePattern.TablePatternInformation> and must be retrieved by using <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCurrentPropertyValue%2A> or <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCachedPropertyValue%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen finnes ikke i <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TablePattern.TablePatternInformation>og må hentes ved hjelp av <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCurrentPropertyValue%2A>eller <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCachedPropertyValue%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCachedPropertyValue%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCurrentPropertyValue%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.TablePattern.TablePatternInformation>

trans-unit.source: This pattern must be from an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement> with an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode> reference in order to get current values.
trans-unit.target: Dette mønsteret må være fra en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>med en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode>referanse for å hente gjeldende verdier.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement> was obtained using <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode>, it contains only cached data, and attempting to get the current value of any property raises an exception.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>ble hentet ved hjelp av <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode>, den inneholder bare bufrede data, og forsøk på å hente gjeldende verdi for en egenskap viser et unntak.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>

trans-unit.source: Use <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TablePattern.Cached%2A> to get the cached value of a property that was previously specified using a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest>.
trans-unit.target: Bruk <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TablePattern.Cached%2A>hente bufrede verdien for en egenskap som ble tidligere definert ved hjelp av en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.TablePattern.Cached%2A>
